1 A BILL for an Act to designate grant funding from the flexible transportation fund; and to provide
2 an exemption.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. FLEXIBLE TRANSPORTATION FUND - EXEMPTION - GRANT - ONE-TIME
5 FUNDING. Notwithstanding the designations and requirements under section 24-02-37.3 and
6 within the limits of legislative appropriations, the director of the department of transportation
7 shall use $3,000,000 from the flexible transportation fund to distribute a grant to a county
8 impacted by a state supreme court case related to a drainage project, during the biennium
9 beginning July 1, 2025, and ending June 30, 2027. The grant funding may be used only for
10 costs associated with a drainage project, including litigation expenses, inflationary costs, and
11 other project costs. The grant funding distributed in this section is considered a one-time
12 funding item.
